<title>zhǔ a nǐ de jiā rén dōu zài zhè lǐ 迦南960</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a nǐ de jiā rén dōu zài zhè lǐ, dōu zhàn zài zhè gè de fāng.
 zhǔ a nǐ lái ba nǐ lái ba. lái dào wǒ men shēn páng.
 tīng jiàn zhǔ cí shēng wèn wǒ men, xiàn zài zěn me yàng.
 pú táo yuán hé chǎng shòu ruò de xiǎo yáng, yǒu méi yǒu kàn wàng.
 zhǔ a zài yī cì shè miǎn wǒ men, b qiú nǐ jiā gěi wǒ men lì liàng.
 wǒ men zhèng yào nǔ lì qián wǎng, zhèng yào nǔ lì qián wǎng.</lyrics>
</song>